In this task, I explored both a coding practice platform and a collaboration tool. I used HackerRank to complete a beginner-level problem, which helped me understand how coding challenges are structured and improved my basic problem-solving approach.
I also created a Google Form to design a digital literacy quiz and analyzed responses using Google Sheets. This gave me insight into how data can be collected and organized efficiently.
Through this task, I realized that coding platforms help in developing logical thinking, while collaboration tools make it easier to manage information and work effectively. I plan to continue practicing on HackerRank and use such tools in my academic work.
